\
All of this is possible\'97even for you! I am no one special. God did some amazing things in my life. And if this is something you want to experience or consider, please, by all means, talk to Him about it. Better yet, email me and ask for more details\'97because I\'92ve only shared the READER\'92S DIGEST VERSION in this article!}